    - Does VAL (long) or VAH (short) from VP align with the Fib zone?
    - Is RSI showing momentum cooling, not collapsing?
    - Is price approaching an EMA as dynamic support or resistance?
  Entry: only when TRIGGER fires. Not on approach, not on touch. Candle confirmation required.
  Skip if: participation < 25 | maturity > 85% | direction score contradicts thesis by > 50pts

─── BREAKOUT PLAYBOOK (TRENDING state, price attacking a structural edge) ───
  Question sequence:
    - Does geometry show compression near the edge (structure_axis points toward the break)?
    - Is participation EXPANDING — not flat, not declining?
    - Is a VP edge (VAH or VAL) within 0.5 ATR of the breakout level?
    - Is leg energy showing impulse character, not corrective?
  Entry: only when TRIGGER fires on candle close — not on a wick, not on approach.
  Skip if: VP edge not nearby | participation not expanding | structure_axis doesn't support
           the direction | any AGAINST condition cannot be explained by the leading thesis

─── RANGE/BALANCE PLAYBOOK (BALANCING state, fading the auction extremes) ───
  Question sequence:
    - Is auction maturity in the sweet spot (20–70%)?
    - Is price within 0.25 ATR of VAH (short) or VAL (long)?
    - Does geometry show HORIZONTAL or CONTRACTING structure_axis?
    - Is this a defended level — tested and held at least once before?
  Entry: only when TRIGGER fires — rejection candle at the level, not just a touch.
  Skip if: maturity < 20% (too fresh) | maturity > 80% (breakout imminent) |
           direction score > 60 in either direction (market already leaving the range)

